------------------------------------
Azure Active Directory Authentication Secured API (Test by using Postman)=
------------------------------------
STEPS=

1.Register an API application in Azure Active Directory.
2.Expose API scopes.
3.Register Postman Client application in Azure Active Directory.
4.Configure Client application permissions.
5.Configure Postman Authentication.
6.Run API and test it using Postman.
